{"type":"text","timestamp":1775867114462,"sessionID":"ses_286140efbffe4OwA8bBtYwNWa0","part":{"id":"prt_d79ed8ba4001ucnUBqEgtCUkb6","messageID":"msg_d79ed56bc001LZOUmzHR5HMetn","sessionID":"ses_286140efbffe4OwA8bBtYwNWa0","type":"text","text":"## Verification Results for AR-021 (CLI build command)\n\n### ✅ **Requirements Met**\n\n1. **Package Layout**: All required files exist and are properly structured\n2. **Console Script Entry Point**: ✓ `kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"` (pyproject.toml:60)\n3. **Typer App Object**: ✓ Correctly configured with proper parameters (main.py:22-28)\n4. **Typer Root Callback**: ✓ Has `--version` and `--verbose` options (main.py:40-51)\n5. **Typer Commands**: All 5 commands implemented (pack, build, publish, invoke, status)\n6. **Pack Command Options**: ✓ All required options present (workspace, agent_name, language, entrypoint, port, build_mode, description, output)\n7. **Build Command**: ✓ Fully implemented with proxy, cloud_provider, output support (main.py:129-176)\n8. **BuildRuntime**: ✓ Complete implementation with version incrementing, local/cloud build modes (build_runtime.py:15-133)\n9. **MetadataOptions**: ✓ Defined as dataclass in pack_models.py:8-25\n10. **AgentMetadata**: ✓ Implemented with proper Pydantic validation (metadata_service.py:15-66)\n11. **Services**: ✓ All services implemented (MetadataService, DockerService, KubernetesProvider, AgentCubeProvider)\n12. **Runtimes**: ✓ All 5 runtimes implemented and exported\n\n### ⚠️ **Minor Deviations**\n\n1. **Missing MetadataOptions Export**: `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` does not re-export `MetadataOptions` as specified (spec says: \"Re-exports runtimes + MetadataOptions\")\n\n### ✅ **Test Results**\n\n- **Tests**: 86 passing, 5 skipped (integration tests requiring Docker)\n- **Coverage**: 54% overall (BuildRuntime: 99%, DockerService: 98%, MetadataService: 93%)\n- **Test Quality**: Comprehensive tests for build runtime including version incrementing, proxy support, cloud builds, and error handling\n\n### ⚠️ **Linting/Type Check**\n\n- **Ruff**: Minor style warnings (unused imports, deprecated typing imports, line length)\n- **Mypy**: Minor type errors related to missing stubs for external libraries (kubernetes, yaml, docker)\n\n### 📊 **API Contract Verification**\n\n- **Build Command CLI**: ✓ All options (`-p/--proxy`, `--cloud-provider`, `--output`) work as specified\n- **BuildRuntime.build()**: ✓ Accepts `workspace_path` and `**options`, returns dict with `image_name`, `image_id`, `image_size`\n- **Version Incrementing**: ✓ Correctly handles semantic versions, prereleases, and custom versions\n- **Error Handling**: ✓ Proper error handling with version rollback on failure\n\n**Summary**: Implementation is substantially complete and functional. All core requirements met. Minor deviation from spec regarding MetadataOptions export in runtime/__init__.py. Tests passing with good coverage.","time":{"start":1775867114458,"end":1775867114458}}}
